    <title>v1.1.0 - 2021-08-12</title>
    <content type="html">
      <ul>
        <li>Change box-shadow color from blue to trimble gray</li>
        <li>Fix for SASS deprecation warnings for adjust-color() saturation</li>
        <li>Change
          <code>&lt;small></code> and
          <code>.small</code> font-size from 10.5px to 12px
        </li>
        <li>Custom Switch CSS fix for IE11</li>
        <li>Drop Edge Legacy support</li>
        <li>Fix for body font-family being duplicated</li>
      </ul>
    </content>
